com.ibm.jaggr.service.config
Interface IConfig.IAlias

Enclosing interface:
IConfig
public static interface IConfig.IAlias

Interface for a config alias. Aliases are resolved by the aggreagtor when building the module dependency graph for the purpose of expanding require list dependencies. In general, any aliases specified in the client loader config should also be specified in the aggregator config.

getReplacement

Object getReplacement()
A string or an implementation specific representation of a JavaScript replacement function.

For javascript replacement functions, the javascript has() function is defined for the feature set provided in the request. The replacement function script may also query the options object which contains the IOptions properties and the initParams object which contains the InitParams properties.

The replacement may be a Script only if getPattern() returns a Pattern.

Returns:
The replacement
